trained to interact with a search engine, python interpreter and mathematical engine, and also improves zero-shot tool use capabilities to interact with potentially unseen tools.\n- **Multilinguality**: Llama 3.2 supports 7 languages in addition to English: French, German, Hindi, Italian, Portuguese, Spanish, and Thai.\n\nFor further details, please refer to the [Llama 3.2 blog](https://ai.meta.com/blog/meta-llama-3-2/) and the [Llama 3.2 model card](https://github.com/meta-llama/llama-models/blob/main/models/llama3_3_2/MODEL_CARD.md).note\n\n## 2. Model Acquisition\n\nYou can access the models on huggingface.\n\n| Data Type | Model Card |\n|:---:|:---:|\n| BF16 | [meta-llama/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct](https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct) |\n| W8A8_INT8 | [RedHatAI/Meta-Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-quantized.w8a8](https://huggingface.co/RedHatAI/M\n\n<!-- REF_TRUNCATED -->\n\nom the dataset.\n- `--random-input 1024`, `--random-output 1024` and `--random-range-ratio 1.0` settings are for fixed 1024-in/1024-out token size limit (realized by truncating or repeating the original sample).\n \nPlease adjust the settings per your benchmarking scenarios. Detailed descriptions for\nthe arguments of `bench_serving` are available\nin [this doc](../../base/benchmarks/lm_benchmark.md).\n\n## Family index.js (full)\n\n### index.js\n```javascript\nimport React from 'react';\nimport ConfigGenerator from '../../base/ConfigGenerator';\n\n/**\n * Llama 3.2 Configuration Generator\n */\nconst Llama32ConfigGenerator = () => {\n  const config = {\n    modelFamily: 'meta-llama',\n\n    options: {\n      hardware: {\n        name: 'hardware',\n        title: 'Hardware Platform',\n        items: [\n          { id: 'cpu', label: 'Xeon CPU', default: true }\n        ]\n      },\n      modelsize: {\n        name: 'modelsize',\n        title: 'Model Size',\n        items: [\n          { id: '8b', label: '8B', default: true }\n        ]\n      },\n      quantization: {\n        name: 'quantization',\n        title: 'Quantization',\n        items: [\n          { id: 'bf16', label: 'BF16', default: true },\n          { id: 'w8a8_int8', label: 'W8A8_INT8', default: false },\n\t  { id: 'fp8', label: 'FP8', default: false },\n\t  { id: 'awq_int4', label: 'AWQ_INT4', default: false },\n        ]\n      },\n    },\n\n    generateCommand: function(values) {\n      const { hardware, modelsize, quantization } = values;\n\n      // Determine model path\n      let modelPath;\n      if (quantization === 'w8a8_int8') {\n\t  modelPath = `RedHatAI/Meta-Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct-quantized.w8a8`;\n\t  } e\n\n<!-- REF_TRUNCATED -->\n\nnable-torch-compile`);\n\t  args.push(`--host 0.0.0.0`);\n\t  args.push(`--tp 6`);\n\n\t  let cmd = 'python -m sglang.launch_server \\\\\\\\\\\\n';\n\t  cmd += `  ${args.join(' \\\\\\\\\\\\n  ')}`;\n\n\t  return cmd;\n    }\n  };\n\n  return <ConfigGenerator config={config} />;\n};\n\nexport default Llama32ConfigGenerator;\n```"}